message:
A vehicle code violation stop by Ontario Police Department turned into arrests by the San Bernardino County Human Trafficking Task Force. "Two Pimping Multiple-Violent-Felony Parolees" were taken into custody on pimping and pandering charges.  The two had prior activities including Car Jacking, Assault with a Firearm, Burglary and Robbery.
